snippet.title: Soulborn - Indie Game Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
Hello Gamers! We are pixelmad studios, a small indie team and here is our alpha trailer for our first game Soulborn to introduce you to our closed-alpha phase you can access (for free) via Discord.

Discord: http://discord.slbrn.com

Web: https://pixelmadstudios.com/project/soulborn

Twitter: https://twitter.com/soulborngame
Facebook: https://facebook.com/soulborngame
Instragram: https://instagram.com/soulborngame
